  <zone type="main">
    <line>Day after day, week after week passed <add place="superlinear">away</add> on</line>
    <line>my return to Geneva and I had not the</line>
    <line>courage to commence my work. I feared the</line>
    <line>vengeance of the disappointed fiend yet</line>
    <line>I <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">could not</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">I was unable to</add>
      </mod> overcome my repugnance <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">to the task</add>
      <mod type="additions">
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear"><metamark>X 1</metamark></add>
      </mod><!--where is the text scholar refers to? we can use <ptr/> to a separate zone, but note that the inserted text 
          source is a letter from William Godwin 
          (the zone is not on this page)--></line>
    <line>My health <del rend="strikethrough">also</del> which had hitherto declined</line>
    <line>was now much restored, &amp; my spirits when</line>
    <line>unchecked by the memory of my unhappy</line>
    <line>promise, rose propor<mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">it</del>
        <add place="intralinear">ti</add>
      </mod>onably. My father</line>
    <line>saw this with pleasure and he turned his</line>
    <line>thoughts towards the best method of</line>
    <line>eradicating the remains of my melancholy &#x2014;</line>
    <line>which every now and then would return</line>
    <line>by fits &amp; with a devouring blackness over</line>
    <line>cast the approaching <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">day</del>
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">sunshine</add>
      </mod>. At these</line>
    <line>moments I took refuge in the most</line>
    <line>perfect solitude: <del rend="strikethrough">&amp; my deli</del>
      <del rend="strikethrough">I used to</del>
      <metamark xml:id="c57-0074.01" rend="transposition" spanTo="#c57-0074.02"
        >Alone<!--lines drawn to <ptr/> location below to indicate transposition--></metamark></line>
    <line>in a little boat I passed whole days on</line>
    <line>the lake watching<metamark xml:id="c57-0074.02"><add><ptr target="#c57-0074.01"
        /></add></metamark> the clouds &amp; <mod type="additions" resp="#pbs">
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">listening to</add>
      </mod> the ripp<mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">les</del>
        <add place="intralinear">ling</add>
      </mod></line>
    <line>of the waves, silent &amp; listless. But the fresh</line>
    <line>air and bright sun seldom failed <add place="intralinear" resp="#pbs">to</add></line>
    <line>restore me to some degree of compo&#x2014;</line>
    <line>sure &amp; <del rend="triple-strike">I</del> on my return I met the</line>
    <line><del rend="strikethough">smi</del> salutations of my friends with a</line>
    <line>readier smile, &amp; <!--resp is unclear--><unclear reason="ambiguous-resp"
        precision="medium"><mod type="additions" resp="#pbs">
          <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
          <add place="superlinear">a</add>
        </mod></unclear> more cheerful heart</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line>It was after my return from one</line>
    <line>of the<add place="intralinear">se</add> rambles that my father calling</line>
    <line>me aside thus a<mod type="additions">
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">d</add>
      </mod>dressed me.</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line>I am happy to remark, my dear</line>
    <line>son, that <del rend="strikethrough">lately</del> you have <del rend="strikethrough"
        >acqu</del></line>
    <line>resumed your former pleasures &amp; seem</line>
    <line>to be returning to yourself. And yet</line>
    <line><del rend="tetra-strike"><unclear reason="illegible" precision="low">so</unclear></del>
      you are still unhappy &amp; still avoid</line>
    <line>our society. <del rend="strikethrough">When I consider</del> For some time</line>
